{"article_id":"h34uzGsv5r1LHRFC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Friday threatened to close the southern border","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"if Democrats do not relent in the standoff over border wall funding ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"which has resulted in a partial government shutdown","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that has lasted a week .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"\" We will be forced to close the Southern Border entirely","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"if the Obstructionist Democrats do not give us the money","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to finish the Wall","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"& also change the ridiculous immigration laws","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"that our Country is saddled with , \"","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"the president tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Mr. Trump previously threatened to close the southern border","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"to stop an approaching migrant caravan .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"The administration did temporarily close a border crossing","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that was being overwhelmed by the caravan .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"In a series of tweets about the border showdown with Democrats , the president said","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"he could justify closing the southern border as a response to the lopsided trade","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"he said","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"the U.S. suffers under the North American Free Trade Agreement .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Mr. Trump also expressed disbelief","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that the U.S. in his view has struggled for so long with porous borders and weak laws","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that foster rampant illegal immigration .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"\" Hard to believe","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"there was a Congress & President","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"who would approve ! \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":3},{"id":26,"text":"White House :","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"Democrats refuse to negotiate","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"as Congress ensures","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"shutdown will last into 2019","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"The standoff over Mr. Trump ' s demand for roughly $ 5 billion for border security","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"including a wall or barrier","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"led to the partial government shutdown , now in its seventh day .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"The shutdown affects 25 percent of the federal government ,","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"including the Interior , Justice and Homeland Security departments .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Acting White House Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney said Friday","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"that the administration proposed an unspecified amount of less than $ 5 billion for the border wall in its most recent offer to Democratic leaders last week ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"but never received a counteroffer .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Mr. Mulvaney said","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"he and Vice President Mike Pence gave Senate Democratic Leader Charles E. Schumer \" a number below five","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"[ $ 5 billion ] \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"during their last face-to-face negotiation .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" I ' m not going to tell you what it is , \"","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"he said of the amount","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"proposed .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"\" We ' re here ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"and they know where to find us , \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Mr. Mulvaney told reporters .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"\" We made an offer last Saturday night","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"[ Dec. 22 ] .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"They told us","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"they ' d get back to us by the end of the week .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"They got back to us last night","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"' We ' re leaving . ' \"","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Democratic leaders insist","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that they support border security","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"but oppose Mr. Trump ' s wall ,","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"it is a costly and ineffective solution to illegal immigration .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"They have backed various alternatives , such as drones and sensors and other high-tech solutions .","depth":4},{"id":61,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"closing the border also could be justified as a response to NAFTA .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"The Trump administration negotiated a rewrite of the three-way deal with Canada and Mexico .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"The new trade pact ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"known as the U.S. Mexico Canada Agreement ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"is awaiting approval by Congress .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"\" The United States loses soooo much money on Trade with Mexico under NAFTA , over 75 Billion Dollars a year","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"( not including Drug Money","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"which would be many times that amount ) ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that I would consider closing the Southern Border a \" profit making operation , ' \"","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"\" We build a Wall","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"or ... close the Southern Border .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Bring our car industry back into the United States","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"where it belongs .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Go back to pre-NAFTA ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"before so many of our companies and jobs were so foolishly sent to Mexico .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Either we build","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"( finish )","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"the Wall","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"or we close the Border , \"","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":165,"left":112,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity